languages.text: "По словам управляющей, последняя сделка была особо удачной и принесла прибыль сверх ожидаемого, в связи с чем станция шлет шаттл с ценными грузами".

traits.locale_text: "По словам управляющей, последняя сделка была особо удачной и принесла прибыль сверх ожидаемого, в связи с чем станция шлет шаттл с ценными грузами".

languages.text: "According to the overseer, the last deal was particularly successful and made a profit beyond expectation, so the station is sending a shuttle of valuable cargo."

languages.text: «De acuerdo con el supervisor, nuestro último trato ha sido particularmente rentable y ha dado mejores resultados de los esperados, por lo que la estación envía una lanzadera con carga valiosa».
languages.original_text: "According to the overseer, the last deal was particularly successful and made a profit beyond expectation, so the station is sending a shuttle of valuable cargo."

languages.text: 「監督者によれば、前回の取引は特に成功裏に終わり、予想以上の利益を上げたことから、ステーションは貴重な貨物のためにシャトルを送ることになったということです」
languages.original_text: "According to the overseer, the last deal was particularly successful and made a profit beyond expectation, so the station is sending a shuttle of valuable cargo."

languages.text: “根据监察员的说法，上次交易大获成功，获得的利润超出了预期。因此，星站准备向我们这边派遣一艘装满贵重物资的穿梭机。”
languages.original_text: "According to the overseer, the last deal was particularly successful and made a profit beyond expectation, so the station is sending a shuttle of valuable cargo."

languages.text: "Dem Aufseher zufolge war das letzte Geschäft ausgesprochen erfolgreich und hat unerwartet hohe Gewinne abgeworfen. Deshalb schickt die Station ein Shuttle mit wertvoller Fracht."
languages.original_text: "According to the overseer, the last deal was particularly successful and made a profit beyond expectation, so the station is sending a shuttle of valuable cargo."

languages.text: « D'après le superviseur, la dernière transaction a été particulièrement fructueuse, la station nous envoie donc une navette chargée de marchandises de valeur. »
languages.original_text: "According to the overseer, the last deal was particularly successful and made a profit beyond expectation, so the station is sending a shuttle of valuable cargo."

languages.text: "Gözetmenin anlattıklarına göre son anlaşma, bilhassa başarılı olarak beklenenin de ötesinde kâr sağlamış. Bu nedenle istasyon, kıymetli kargolar içeren bir mekik gönderiyor."
languages.original_text: "According to the overseer, the last deal was particularly successful and made a profit beyond expectation, so the station is sending a shuttle of valuable cargo."
